WorkItem.Description:
Compiling this code with the latest build of the compiler in the develop branch results in the error:
```
                try {

                } catch (ex1) {

                }

                try {

                } catch (ex1) {

                }
```
>  error TS2000: Duplicate identifier 'ex1'.

According to the Section 12.14 of the EcmaScript language specification, the catch block introduces a new LexicalEnvironment. Therefore, these declarations should not collide.
